title: "Multimodal safety monitor"
excerpt: " This project was focused on building a multimodal safety monitor by combining two unsafe
systems; a vision-based AI system and real-time localization system (RTLS).
o Wrote python algorithms to facilitate the integration of the vision system and the RTLS system to facilitate exchange of
